description: Warrior Princess takes on the Amazon. The Amazon, with two losses, has shown the most improvement of any wrestler. She gets stronger as the match goes on and adapts better then anyone. The Warrior Princess has only lost one match, and is looking forward to beating the young upstart Amazon. It was agreed at the start that the loser would get ass fucked by the winner. US history was made during this match, as one wrestler fought back and won after losing the first two rounds. Who gets it in the ass? You just have to watch to find out.
title: Xana (1-1) vs. Hollie (0-2)
